{"tid":1928707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：收費安排不適用於湖北返港的人士","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T14:42:45.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edcb8a245bd728bb4a306319c48b81a14066d91e","tid":1928707,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"政府澄清關於向隔離人士收費的安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就有報道評論政府不應「一刀切」向所有強制隔離人士收費，政府發言人今日（三月十六日）澄清並無此安排。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人説，有關收費安排只適用於入住政府的暫住設施，即曹公潭戶外康樂中心、西貢戶外康樂中心或麥理浩夫人度假村。入住的人士都是從國內（除湖北省以外）返港的香港居民，應該在家居或其自行安排的處所進行家居隔離。此收費安排不適用於入住檢疫中心的人士，即與確診患者有密切接觸，或由健康風險較高的地區（如湖北省）抵港但沒有出現病徵的人士。<span style=\"color: red;\">因此，從日本鑽石公主號或湖北返港的人士入住檢疫中心是毋須收費的</span>。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年3月16日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間22時00分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/16/P2020031600778.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F16%2FP2020031600778.htm&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=e6ace5d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/16/P2020031600778.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf60faad74f2293e55659a6f98b7bc440d06e446","tid":1928707,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da5255720f9c46cbc7d2aff510405055fc405c6","tid":1928707,"uid":141668,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"港共: <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">湖北獨立，正式啟動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6df1fc656daa7ffdf217caab2e4dfa48adfa9d","tid":1928707,"uid":331949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:09:47.000Z","msg":"歐洲翻嚟嘅香港人呢？"},{"pid":"2f77fd2d13bf